## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="6e6bf-103">因为基于任务的异步编程模型往往抽象的线程，使用<xref:System.Threading.AsyncLocal%601>实例可用于跨线程保存数据。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6e6bf-103">Because the task-based asynchronous programming model tends to abstract the use of threads, <xref:System.Threading.AsyncLocal%601> instances can be used to persist data across threads.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="6e6bf-104"><xref:System.Threading.AsyncLocal%601>类还提供可选的通知时与关联的值的当前的线程更改，或者因为显式更改通过设置<xref:System.Threading.AsyncLocal%601.Value%2A>属性，或隐式更改时的线程遇到`await`或其他上下文转换。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6e6bf-104">The <xref:System.Threading.AsyncLocal%601> class also provides optional notifications when the value associated with the current thread changes, either because it was explicitly changed by setting the <xref:System.Threading.AsyncLocal%601.Value%2A> property, or implicitly changed when the thread encountered an `await` or other context transition.</span></span>  
  
   
  
